{"tha-ap165:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap165:0.2":"Suparicariyavagga ","tha-ap165:0.3":"Khajjakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap165:1.1":"“Tissassa kho bhagavato, ","tha-ap165:1.2":"pubbe phalamadasaham; ","tha-ap165:1.3":"Nalikeranca padasim, ","tha-ap165:1.4":"khajjakam abhisammatam. ","tha-ap165:2.1":"Buddhassa tamaham datva, ","tha-ap165:2.2":"Tissassa tu mahesino; ","tha-ap165:2.3":"Modamaham kamakami, ","tha-ap165:2.4":"Upapajjim yamicchakam. ","tha-ap165:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap165:3.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap165:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap165:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap165:4.1":"Ito terasakappamhi, ","tha-ap165:4.2":"raja indasamo ahu; ","tha-ap165:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap165:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap165:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap165:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap165:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap165:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma khajjakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap165:7.1":"Khajjakadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}